metadata.name: Purple Diamond
metadata.description:
This artwork is created by a 3 year-old girl, SANA, and colored by SANA with her pure, fun, energetic, innocent and yet unintentional mind. 

No one can make anything the same as or similar to this, even SANA herself. She keeps growing up and will gradually expose herself to the society, which makes it hard for her to retain this status of mind. 

Physical-wise and time-wise, This artwork is her “one and only” , so I titled this “Purple Diamond”.

Pixel Dimension: 10000 × 7084px
Resolution: 300 dpi
